{
  "stem": "16930.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I can't think of the name right now.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It will come back to me while we're talking, and got that regular high school diploma in February-- February 1957.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I also entered college in February '57, City College in New York.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Because you had-- for City College, you had to have a regular high school diploma.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "My-- my equivalency didn't count.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They wouldn't count that, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And so I had to get a regular high school diploma.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I got that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Based upon some-- they transferred the stuff that I did in Israel through the correspondence course, they transferred that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But I had to take a couple-- I had to take American history and civics.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "There were several things I had to take-- so-- in the high school, and a few subjects to get my high school diploma.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I got that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And then I got a job, a different-- different job, different Sunday jobs.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And then in 1959-- I'm going to go through it quickly, because you're running out of time-- I got a job as a Hebrew teacher, [?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Tamil ?] Torah, afternoon schools.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Kids go to school in daytime, and go to school to-- to a Hebrew school in the afternoon.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "It's not on a very high level.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And I was able to handle that, based partly on my-- the foundation I got in that group home.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And also I knew Hebrew pretty well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I was learning on my own subsequently, and I was able to be a Hebrew teacher.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And I did that from 1959 through 1964-- till 1963, till 1960-- I think it was 1960-- 1963.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And it was '64, I think it was '64, 1964.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "It was five years.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And then I came back to London.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
